{"tid":1540241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外國文宣：twitter 全民hashtag #FiveDemands","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:03:04.000Z","uid":234159,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a127b7c90fdbce543a6527fa20c0d5ce343f345d","tid":1540241,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"各位手足 廢話唔多講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n外國人隔岸觀火，以為我地贏咗，咁的輿論是好不利的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全世界！馬上save呢張圖（可唔可有人整到張英文版），<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/du5Xin6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdu5Xin6.jpg&h=d312297e&s={SIZE}\" />然後hastag #FiveDemands </span></span><br />\n<br />\nOur five demands:<br />\n1/ Completely withdraw Extradition Bill.<br />\n2/ Retract the proclamation that protests on 9th June and 12th June were riots<br />\n3/ Withdraw criminal charges against all protesters <br />\n4/ Thoroughly investigate abuse of powers by the police.<br />\n5/ Dissolve the Legislative Council by administrative order, and immediately implement Dual Universal Suffrage.<br />\n<br />\n手足，佔咗79日，我地咩都無；7條命、1000人被捕、3隻眼、無數人被打至永久傷殘，終於換來<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個</span></span>撤回，好淒涼，亦是我地見到曙光的開始！唔好放棄，齊上齊落！"},{"pid":"7cb622c2d5999b0db2cce7a1fd07c8139fe7f02c","tid":1540241,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"請幫推，巴絲"},{"pid":"b38a02fd231071f099ccf04e569ab8f9bcaf506f","tid":1540241,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7a057375919e2174028e5998b0ce0551755ce2e","tid":1540241,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba32f642894de0dab0d6067c973911b66a6c6364","tid":1540241